{"data":{"pagesYaml":{"intro":"Having a problem with the IRS taking too much of your stash? At Red Eye CPA we focus on Section 280E mitigation and make sure you get as much tax benefit as you legally can.","page":"about","team":[{"name":"Daria Nagal","position":"CPA, EA","desc":"Daria Nagal is a California CPA and an Enrolled Agent. She comes from Public Accounting, where she primarily focused on the taxation of small businesses, real estate entities, and high-net-worth individuals. \n\nDaria learned all ins and outs of the Cannabis Industry at a six-store dispensary chain, where she oversaw the accounting functions as well as local tax compliance. At Red Eye CPA Daria is in charge of income tax preparation, section 280 E mitigation, and local taxes.","photo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/88e20/about_daria.jpg","srcSet":"/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/86e11/about_daria.jpg 100w,\n/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/f836f/about_daria.jpg 200w,\n/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/88e20/about_daria.jpg 395w","srcWebp":"/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/d5ecf/about_daria.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/d1f52/about_daria.webp 100w,\n/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/61e93/about_daria.webp 200w,\n/static/bddea96ea8076e74a1ce15ffb8c6c79a/d5ecf/about_daria.webp 395w","sizes":"(max-width: 395px) 100vw, 395px"}}}},{"name":"Helena Gregory","position":"Senior Accountant","desc":"Helena has over ten years of various accounting experience. She has worked on the audit side of public accounting and held a couple of senior accountant positions in the banking and tourism industries.\n\nHelena is a Quickbooks expert and an accounting wizard. At Red Eye CPA, she is in charge of bookkeeping and preparation of financial statements.","photo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/s